title: As Roger Federer Retires, Two Great Rivalries Come to an End
description: A look at the great matches between Federer and Rafael Nadal as well as Federer and Novak Djokovic.
dc:creator: Jesus Jiménez
media:description: Roger Federer, right, shaking hands with Novak Djokovic during a practice session on Thursday ahead of the Laver Cup while on the court with Rafael Nadal, wearing a white hat.
